TITLE: Implementing updateBio resolver with Prisma Client
DESCRIPTION: Implementation of the updateBio mutation resolver using Prisma Client. This resolver updates a user's profile bio by using the nested update functionality to modify the related profile record.
SOURCE: https://github.com/prisma/docs/blob/main/content/200-orm/800-more/300-upgrade-guides/800-upgrade-from-prisma-1/06-upgrading-prisma-binding-to-sdl-first.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_26

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const resolvers = {
  Mutation: {
    //highlight-start
    updateBio: (_, args, context, info) => {
      return context.prisma.user.update({
        data: {
          profile: {
            update: { bio: args.bio },
          },
        },
        where: args.userUniqueInput,
      })
    },
    //highlight-end
    // ... other resolvers
  },
}
```

