TITLE: Enforcing @unique for One-to-One Relations in Prisma ORM 4
DESCRIPTION: These code snippets demonstrate how to properly define one-to-one relations between User and Profile models in Prisma ORM 4, where the @unique attribute must be added to relation fields in both relational databases and MongoDB.
SOURCE: https://github.com/prisma/docs/blob/main/content/200-orm/800-more/300-upgrade-guides/200-upgrading-versions/700-upgrading-to-prisma-4.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_5

