TITLE: Generating Baseline Migration SQL with Prisma CLI - Terminal
DESCRIPTION: These commands generate a baseline migration SQL file based on your current database schema, and then mark the migration as applied in Prisma. Use --from-empty to indicate there are no prior migrations, and --script to output executable SQL. Replace paths as appropriate to fit your directory structure.
SOURCE: https://github.com/prisma/docs/blob/main/content/800-guides/040-migrate-from-sequelize.mdx#_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: terminal
