TITLE: Migrating User Query Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Updated implementation of the user query with new Prisma Client API syntax and input types.
SOURCE: https://github.com/prisma/docs/blob/main/content/200-orm/800-more/300-upgrade-guides/800-upgrade-from-prisma-1/04-upgrading-nexus-prisma-to-nexus.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_21

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const Query = queryType({
  definition(t) {
    t.field('user', {
      type: 'User',
      args: {
        userUniqueInput: arg({
          type: 'UserUniqueInput',
          nullable: false,
        }),
      },
      resolve: (_, args, context) => {
        return context.prisma.user.findUnique({
          where: {
            id: args.userUniqueInput?.id,
            email: args.userUniqueInput?.email,
          },
        })
      },
    })
  },
})
```

