TITLE: Migrating Posts Query Implementation
DESCRIPTION: Updated implementation of the posts query with new Prisma Client API syntax.
SOURCE: https://github.com/prisma/docs/blob/main/content/200-orm/800-more/300-upgrade-guides/800-upgrade-from-prisma-1/04-upgrading-nexus-prisma-to-nexus.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_20

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
queryType({
  definition(t) {
    t.list.field('posts', {
      type: 'Post',
      args: {
        searchString: stringArg({ nullable: true }),
      },
      resolve: (parent, { searchString }, context) => {
        return context.prisma.post.findMany({
          where: {
            OR: [
              { title: { contains: searchString } },
              { content: { contains: searchString } },
            ],
          },
        })
      },
    })
  },
})
```

