TITLE: Initial Prisma Schema for Users and Posts Models
DESCRIPTION: Define MongoDB models with relations using Prisma schema, including references between users, posts, and categories
SOURCE: https://github.com/prisma/docs/blob/main/content/800-guides/050-migrate-from-mongoose.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: prisma
CODE:
```
type UsersProfile {
  bio String
}

model categories {
  id   String @id @default(auto()) @map("_id") @db.ObjectId
  v    Int    @map("__v")
  name String
}

model posts {
  id        String  @id @default(auto()) @map("_id") @db.ObjectId
