CODE:
```
await prisma.MailBox.createMany({
  data: [
    {
      name: 'Alice',
      addresses: {
        set: [
          {
            address: 'alice@prisma.io', // Not unique
          },
          {
            address: 'alice@prisma.io', // Not unique
          },
        ],
      },
    },
  ],
})
