SOURCE: https://github.com/prisma/docs/blob/main/content/200-orm/800-more/600-help-and-troubleshooting/800-check-constraints.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_1

LANGUAGE: sql
CODE:
```
CREATE TABLE "public"."product" (
  price NUMERIC CONSTRAINT price_value_check CHECK (price > 0.01 AND price <> 1240.00)
);
ALTER TABLE "public"."product"
  ADD COLUMN "productid" serial,
  ADD PRIMARY KEY ("productid");
```

