TITLE: Fixing Incorrect m-n Relations in MySQL for Prisma ORM 2
DESCRIPTION: SQL statements to fix 1-n relations that were incorrectly recognized as m-n. This includes adding a foreign key column, migrating data from the relation table, and dropping the unnecessary relation table.
