TITLE: Prisma 1 GraphQL Data Model Definition
DESCRIPTION: A Prisma 1 data model written in GraphQL SDL defining User, Post, Profile, and Category types with their relationships and field directives.
SOURCE: https://github.com/prisma/docs/blob/main/content/200-orm/800-more/300-upgrade-guides/800-upgrade-from-prisma-1/03-upgrading-the-prisma-layer-postgresql.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_7

