TITLE: Correcting the Employee model with NoAction referential actions in Prisma
DESCRIPTION: This updated Prisma schema for the Employee model explicitly sets onDelete and onUpdate actions to NoAction. This resolves the validation error by preventing cycles in referential actions for the self-relation.
