TITLE: Configuring Turborepo task dependencies
DESCRIPTION: This JSON configuration for turbo.json sets up task dependencies, ensuring that database-related tasks are executed before build and dev tasks. It optimizes the workflow in the monorepo setup.
SOURCE: https://github.com/prisma/docs/blob/main/content/800-guides/080-turborepo.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_15

LANGUAGE: json
CODE:
```
{
  "$schema": "https://turbo.build/schema.json",
  "ui": "tui",
  "tasks": {
    "build": {
      "dependsOn": ["^build", "^db:generate"],
      "inputs": ["$TURBO_DEFAULT$", ".env*"],
      "outputs": [".next/**", "!.next/cache/**"]
    },
    "lint": {
      "dependsOn": ["^lint"]
    },
    "check-types": {
      "dependsOn": ["^check-types"]
    },
    "dev": {
      "dependsOn": ["^db:generate"],
      "cache": false,
      "persistent": true
    },
    "db:generate": {
      "cache": false
    },
    "db:migrate": {
      "cache": false,
      "persistent": true
    },
    "db:deploy": {
      "cache": false
    }
  }
}
```

