TITLE: Long-running transaction in Prisma with TypeScript
DESCRIPTION: This code snippet demonstrates a long-running transaction using Prisma's `$transaction` API. It performs multiple operations, including creating an order, updating a user's balance, and creating a shipping record, within a single transaction. This pattern can lead to database locks, connection tie-ups, and other performance issues.
