TITLE: Resolver Implementation for addPostToCategories with Nexus
DESCRIPTION: TypeScript implementation of the resolver for addPostToCategories using Prisma ORM 2.0 with Nexus. It connects a post to multiple categories using the Prisma client.
SOURCE: https://github.com/prisma/docs/blob/main/content/200-orm/800-more/300-upgrade-guides/800-upgrade-from-prisma-1/05-upgrading-prisma-binding-to-nexus.mdx#_snippet_44

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const Mutation = mutationType({
  definition(t) {
    // ... mutations from before
    t.field('addPostToCategories', {
      type: 'Post',
      args: {
        postId: stringArg({ nullable: false }),
        categoryIds: stringArg({
          list: true,
          nullable: false,
        }),
      },
      //add-start
      resolve: (_, args, context) => {
        const ids = args.categoryIds.map((id) => ({ id }))
        return context.prisma.post.update({
          where: {
            id: args.postId,
          },
          data: {
            categories: { connect: ids },
          },
        })
      },
      //add-end
    })
  },
})
```

