TITLE: MongoDB View Creation Command
DESCRIPTION: MongoDB command to create a UserInfo view using aggregation pipeline
SOURCE: https://github.com/prisma/docs/blob/main/content/200-orm/100-prisma-schema/20-data-model/40-views.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
db.createView('UserInfo', 'User', [
  {
    $lookup: {
      from: 'Profile',
      localField: '_id',
      foreignField: 'userId',
      as: 'ProfileData',
    },
  },
  {
    $project: {
      _id: 1,
      email: 1,
      name: 1,
      bio: '$ProfileData.bio',
    },
  },
  { $unwind: '$bio' },
])
```

