TITLE: Explicit Many-to-Many Self Relation
DESCRIPTION: Defines an explicit many-to-many self-relation using an intermediate Follows model to store additional relationship data.
SOURCE: https://github.com/prisma/docs/blob/main/content/200-orm/100-prisma-schema/20-data-model/20-relations/400-self-relations.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_3

LANGUAGE: prisma
CODE:
```
model User {
  id         Int       @id @default(autoincrement())
  name       String?
  followedBy Follows[] @relation("followedBy")
  following  Follows[] @relation("following")
}

model Follows {
  followedBy   User @relation("followedBy", fields: [followedById], references: [id])
  followedById Int
  following    User @relation("following", fields: [followingId], references: [id])
  followingId  Int

  @@id([followingId, followedById])
}
```

