TITLE: Defining Multi-Field Unique Constraint in Prisma Schema (Relational)
DESCRIPTION: Example showing how to define a custom-named unique constraint across multiple fields in a User model for relational databases.
SOURCE: https://github.com/prisma/docs/blob/main/content/200-orm/500-reference/100-prisma-schema-reference.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_51

LANGUAGE: prisma
CODE:
