TITLE: Implementing Post Type Resolver with Prisma Client
DESCRIPTION: This code demonstrates how to implement the type resolver for the Post type, resolving the 'author' and 'categories' relations using Prisma Client.
SOURCE: https://github.com/prisma/docs/blob/main/content/200-orm/800-more/300-upgrade-guides/800-upgrade-from-prisma-1/06-upgrading-prisma-binding-to-sdl-first.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_14

LANGUAGE: javascript
CODE:
```
const resolvers = {
  Query: {
    // ... your query resolvers
  },
  Mutation: {
    // ... your mutation resolvers
  },
  User: {
    // ... your type resolvers for `User` from before
  },
  Post: {
    author: (parent, args, context) => {
      return context.prisma.post
        .findUnique({
          where: { id: parent.id },
        })
        .author()
    },
    categories: (parent, args, context) => {
      return context.prisma.post
        .findUnique({
          where: { id: parent.id },
        })
        .categories()
    },
  },
}
```

