DESCRIPTION: This snippet demonstrates how to set a custom location for the Prisma format engine binary using the PRISMA_FMT_BINARY environment variable. Note that this functionality has been removed in Prisma CLI version 4.10.0 and only works in earlier versions.
SOURCE: https://github.com/prisma/docs/blob/main/content/200-orm/500-reference/300-environment-variables-reference.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_5

LANGUAGE: env
CODE:
```
PRISMA_FMT_BINARY=custom/my-custom-format-engine-unix
```

