TITLE: Fetching Relations with Sequelize
DESCRIPTION: Shows how to fetch a record with its related records in Sequelize using the include option. This example retrieves a user and includes their related posts.
SOURCE: https://github.com/prisma/docs/blob/main/content/200-orm/800-more/400-comparisons/02-prisma-and-sequelize.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_4

LANGUAGE: typescript
CODE:
```
const user = await User.findByPk(id, {
  include: [
    {
      model: Post,
    },
  ],
})
```

