TITLE: Prisma Datamodel with UpdatedAt Annotation
DESCRIPTION: Depicts a Prisma 1 datamodel using `@updatedAt` directive for runtime-managed `DateTime` fields, which lack direct reflection in database migrations.
SOURCE: https://github.com/prisma/docs/blob/main/content/200-orm/800-more/300-upgrade-guides/800-upgrade-from-prisma-1/02-schema-incompatibilities-postgresql.mdx#2025-04-21_snippet_11

LANGUAGE: graphql
CODE:
```
type Post {
  id: ID! @id
  updatedAt: DateTime! @updatedAt
}
```

